Change Log
==========

v0.4.1: Fri, 19 Apr 2013 07:33:29 +0100
    * Minor bug fix with construtor in Sound and Music.

v0.4.0: Wed, 17 Apr 2013 21:02:19 +0100
    * Target compiler is now gcc-4.8.
    * Removed calls to SDL_GetTicks().
    * New open/close initialization convention.
    * Stream functions for Surfaces.
    * Improved error control for Surface load.
    * Surface, Music, Sound objects now have reference counted data.
    * Added make_independent_copy() function to Surface.
    * New set of constructors for Surface, Music, Sound.
    * Debug logging that can be turned on with #DEBUG_LOG

v0.3.0: Sat, 30 Mar 2013 21:39:26 +0000: Jon Haggblad <jon@haeggblad.com>
    * Updated all functions to the new naming convention. Should mean that the
      interface is relatively stable (for now).

v0.2.0: Tue, 05 Mar 2013 17:43:03 +0000: Jon Haggblad <jon@haeggblad.com>

    * Moved all classes to sdlc namespace.
    * Added a global SDLc.h header file.
    * Misc fixes.
    * Started the migration to intrinsic c++ type.

v0.1.0: Tue, 12 Feb 2013 18:03:31 +0000: Jon Haggblad <jon@haeggblad.com>

    * First release separate from Kexx2.
    * Minor code cleanup.


